name: Ki-La
description: Goddess of Ur-80, guardian of colour and shape, Ki-la is ready to leave for the Night of the Queens. The most crucial event in the Metagalaxy that takes place every 1000 years since the dawn of time. The moment where she will find her sisters, the daughters of the void, is nearby. The keepers of the cosmos reunite again for the embrace of the origin, to grantee the light in the stars of the universe for another millennium.
